<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sensible-adj">sensible <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sensəbl/    美 /'sensəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-wise">1.★ <strong>明智的；合理的(wise)；可觉察到的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a sensible answer / option 
明智的回答/选择</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He did not appear to <strong>be sensible of</strong> the difficulties that lay ahead. 
他看上去并没有意识到面前的困难。</p></div></div>